events.name: Startup Pitch Night
events.description: Pitch your startup ideas to a panel of investors and industry experts. Network with fellow entrepreneurs and gain valuable feedback on your business.

events.name: Music Festival 2024
events.description: Experience live performances from top bands and artists at our annual Music Festival. A day of great music, food, and fun awaits!

events.name: Food Truck Rally
events.description: Enjoy a variety of delicious food from local food trucks at our Food Truck Rally. Live music and entertainment will be provided.

events.name: Literary Festival
events.description: Attend author readings, book signings, and literary discussions at our Literary Festival. Meet your favorite authors and discover new reads.

events.name: Film Screening & Q&A
events.description: Watch a special screening of an acclaimed film followed by a Q&A session with the director. An evening of cinema and conversation awaits.

events.name: New Year's Eve Gala
events.description: Ring in the New Year with style at our Gala. Enjoy a night of dancing, dining, and celebrations as we welcome 2025.
